here of Lalitā-sakhī.

9
00:00:46,970 --> 00:01:01,450
And what is he signified 
as important that She possesses

10
00:01:01,450 --> 00:01:10,183
the greatest magnitude of eagerness 
for the list aspect of sevā,

11
