15
00:01:29,326 --> 00:01:37,919
when that one brāhmaṇ devotee, 
he writes some śloka

16
00:01:37,919 --> 00:01:42,509
in praise of Jagannāth
and Mahāprabhu.

17
00:01:42,509 --> 00:01:46,679
